Trimage (image compressor for optimizing PNG and JPG files)

Trimage is a cross-platform GUI and command-line interface to optimize
image files via "optipng",  "advpng" and "jpegoptim", depending on the
filetype  (currently,  PNG and JPG files).  Image files are losslessly
compressed on the highest available compression levels.  Trimage gives
you  various input functions to fit your own workflow:  A regular file
dialog, dragging and dropping and various command line options.

http://trimage.org